GroupResourceType
description: The supported resource types that can be used as values of +group_resource.resource_type+. +INSTANCE+ includes +gce_instance+ and +aws_ec2_instance+ resource types. The resource types +gae_app+ and +uptime_url+ are not valid here because group checks on App Engine modules and URLs are not allowed.
